      "beast_baseline": "peace in the release of the mask... that's a weird way to put it. but i guess i get what you mean. it just feels like i'm exhausted from pretending. if the person everyone thinks i am is just a fake, then what's the point of all this effort? why keep up a lie if there's nobody actually behind it?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
